==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Quilling
<hw>Quill"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>A band
of linen, muslin, or the like, fluted, folded, or plaited so as somewhat
to resemble a row of quills.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>One of the rounded
plaits or flutings of such a band.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Quillwort</ent>⟦br⟧
